post_install() {
  cat <<-EOF

  You will need to enable the two plugins, "BackgroundZoom" and "AppearanceEditor"
by opening a Terminator window and right-clicking the vte widget for the popup
terminal menu->Preferences->Plugins - place a check in the box beside each one.
The Dbus server in the main Preferences dialog must be unchecked.
EOF
}
